g.text: For each 15-minute interval in the day (total of 96)
MaxSolarProduction = energy generated by the solar panel
Split solar energy into EnergyForUsage and EnergyForBattery
Limited by the battery's maximum capacity
Limited by the battery's maximum capacity
ChargeLevel = Previous level + 15min * (ChargeEfficiency * BatteryCharge - BatteryDischarge / DischargeEfficiency)
UserUsage = EnergyForUsage + BatteryDischarge + EnergyPurchased - EnergySold + EnergyReceived - EnergySent
Store EnergyPurchased, EnergySold, ChargeLevel, BatteryCharge, BatteryDischarge, EnergyForUsage, EnergyForBattery, EnergyReceived, EnergySent
FinalChargeLevel = ChargeLevel at the last interval
Save final ChargeLevel for the day
Total Cost = Sum(PurchasePrice * EnergyPurchased - SellingPrice * EnergySold) for all intervals
